# Quality Gate

Before completing any task that changes code in this repository:

- Run `uv run ruff check .`.
- Run `uv run mypy .`.
- Fix all reported issues in the changed code before marking the task complete.
- Do not skip these checks because a change seems small.

If `mypy` is missing from the environment, install or add it first so the check can run.
